<h2>Run CAP3 program for Sequence Assembly</h2>
<strong>Important:</strong>
If the file of reads is named ' xyz ', then the file of quality values must be named ' xyz.qual ',and the file of constraints named ' xyz.con '.</br></br>

 
<form method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data" action="cap3.php">

